    <p>{`If your account has access to the Teams feature, escalation policies are designed to connect other core PagerDuty objects to your Teams. When you add an escalation policy to a Team, all of the escalation policy's associated users, schedules and services will be assigned to that Team. For more information, please check out our `}<a parentName="p" {...{
