    <ul>
      <li parentName="ul">{`You can add up to 20 escalation rules to an escalation policy.`}
        <ul parentName="li">
          <li parentName="ul">{`You have the option to repeat an escalation policy 9 times. Once an escalation policy reaches the amount of loops configured, the incident will stay assigned to the last user and will not continue to notify once it has cycled through all of the responder's contact methods.`}</li>
          <li parentName="ul">{`Notifying too many users at once runs the risk of creating confusion about who owns an incident. With this is mind, `}<a parentName="li" {...{
