            }}>{`This topic`}</a>{` addresses best practices about when to notify one user vs. many users.`}</li>
          <li parentName="ul">{`The minimum escalation timeout is 1 minute if there is a single target on an escalation rule. Alternatively, if there is more than one target in an escalation level the minimum escalation timeout is 5 minutes. These restrictions are displayed in the web UI.`}</li>
