      <p parentName="blockquote">{`No. Please visit `}<a parentName="p" {...{
          "href": "https://support.pagerduty.com/docs/escalation-policies-and-schedules#section-why-schedules-alone-are-ineffective-for-multi-user-notifications"
        }}>{`Why Schedules Alone Are Ineffective For Multi-User Notifications`}</a>{` for more information. This section covers essential concepts to understand, and how to properly configure multi-user notifications.`}</p>
