          }}></path></svg></a>{`On Call Handoff Notification Settings`}</h2>
    <p>{`On-call hand off notifications (OCHONs) can notify users on the escalation policy up to 48 hours before they go on-call, off-call, or both. These notifications can only be sent as an SMS, push notification, or email. You can configure settings for when your escalation policy will send on call handoff notifications. `}</p>
